          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/04/248396185/10316b5178d5109d597f415d6e7903dc_7597794524846042368.png",
                "id": "talent8002",
                "key": "Tempered Sword",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Tempered Sword"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: #FF9999\">Pyro DMG</span>. For the third use of this Skill each Round, deals +2 DMG.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/04/248396185/d0e27bc7054292e95c673e6f491ff677_3729784084901709977.png",
                "id": "talent61859",
                "key": "Searing Onslaught",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Searing Onslaught"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 8 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span>. This character gains <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pyro Infusion</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Pyro Infusion</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br>The character to which this is attached has their <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span> dealt converted to<span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/04/248396185/7f35364dc83b6694a3200aae53f6670f_6972509467247254536.png",
                "id": "talent50184",
                "key": "Dawn",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Dawn"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Pyro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 for this instance, the target is forcibly switched to the next character</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning Flame</span>] that will deal 1 Pyro DMG at the end of the Round (Takes effect once, max 2 stacks)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/05/77454259/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_3135645163697502884.png",
                "id": "talent15289",
                "key": "Pyro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Pyro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Duration (Rounds)</span></strong></p><p>Each time you reach the end of a Round, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds) </span>-1.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds)</span> runs out.</p><p><br></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/15/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_2735958786086240694.png",
                "id": "talent31238",
